    "spell_type": "spell",
    "rank": 3,
    "text": "You unleash a holy beam of freezing moonlight. Make a ranged spell attack. The ray deals 5d6 cold damage. If the target has the unholy trait, you deal an extra 5d6 spirit damage. Moonlight ray\u2019s cold damage is silver damage for the purposes of weaknesses, resistances, and the like.",
